default/files/web_zuerich_towers_los_carpinteros_1280x960_21982.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-11-07 16:46:44 +0100','Erstellt aus Schweizer Stein','Made from Swiss stone','Construit à partir de briques suisses','Realizzata con pietre svizzere',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'CH','Zürich',8005,'Escher-Wyss-Platz','https://www.zuerich.com/node/227368',47.391070400000,8.522275500000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
