tfreunde. Heute beherbergt das Haus die Sammlung Arthur und Hedy Hahnloser-Bühler, zu der Werke von Manet, Cézanne und van Gogh gehören.</p><p>Die Villa Flora wird nach einem Umbau voraussichtlich 2022 wiedereröffnet.</p>','<p>Since the merger of the former Kunstmuseum Winterthur, the Museum Oskar Reinhart, and the Villa Flora, the newly formed umbrella brand, Kunst Museum Winterthur, houses one of the most beautiful art collections in Switzerland.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Beim Stadthaus</span></p><p>The former Kunstmuseum is the oldest of Winterthur&rsquo;s art museums. Opened in 1916, it continues to expand its collection of paintings, sculptures, drawings, and prints. Nowadays, the museum holds the fourth largest public collection of modern art in Switzerland.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Reinhart am Stadtgarten</span></p><p>When it opened in 1951, the former Museum Oskar Reinhart was the first private museum in Switzerland. The collection of patron Oskar Reinhart (1885-1965) includes Swiss, German and Austrian art of early Romanticism and Realism. The museum also exhibits masterpieces from the Dutch Golden Age.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Villa Flora</span></p><p>The residence of the collector couple, Hahnloser-Bühler, was once a meeting place for artists and art lovers. These days, it houses Arthur and Hedy Hahnloser-Bühler&rsquo;s art collection, which includes works by Manet, Cézanne, and van Gogh.</p><p>The Villa Flora is currently closed for renovation and is expected to reopen in 2022.</p>','<p>Depuis que l&rsquo;ancien musée d&rsquo;art, le musée Oskar Reinhart et la Villa Flora se sont regroupés, le musée des Beaux-Arts de Winterthour dispose de l&rsquo;une des plus belles collections d&rsquo;art de Suisse.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Près du Stadthaus</span></p><p>Ce musée d&rsquo;art est le plus ancien de Winterthour. Inauguré en 1916, il a depuis constamment agrandi sa collection de tableaux, sculptures, dessins et illustrations. Le musée dispose aujourd&rsquo;hui de la 4e plus grande collection publique d&rsquo;art moderne de Suisse.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Le Reinhart dans le jardin de la cité</span></p><p>Inauguré en 1951, l&rsquo;ancien musée Oskar Reinhart fut le premier musée privé de Suisse. La collection du mécène Oskar Reinhart (1885-1965) rassemble les arts suisse, allemand et autrichien du réalisme et du préromantisme. On y découvre également les maîtres néerlandais de l&rsquo;âge d&rsquo;or.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Villa Flora</span></p><p>La maison du couple de collectionneurs Hahnloser-Bühler fut le lieu de rencontre des artistes et des amateurs d&rsquo;art. L&rsquo;édifice abrite aujourd&rsquo;hui la collection d&rsquo;Arthur et Hedy Hahnloser-Bühler avec des œuvres de Manet, Cézanne et van Gogh.</p><p>La Villa Flora rouvrira probablement en 2022 après quelques travaux.</p>','<p>Dall&rsquo;unione di Kunstmuseum, Museo Oskar Reinhart e Villa Flora è nato il Kunst Museum Winterthur, che vanta una delle più belle collezioni d&rsquo;arte del mondo.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Beim Stadthaus</span></p><p>L&rsquo;ex Kunstmuseum è il più antico tra le case d&rsquo;arte di Winterthur. Inaugurato nel 1916, propone una collezione di dipinti, sculture, disegni e grafiche in costante crescita. Oggi, la struttura vanta la quarta più grande collezione pubblica di arte moderna della Svizzera.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Reinhart am Stadtgarten</span></p><p>In occasione della sua inaugurazione, nel 1951, l&rsquo;ex Museo Oskar Reinhart fu il primo museo privato della Svizzera. La collezione del mecenate Oskar Reinhart (1885-1965) comprende arte elvetica, tedesca e austriaca del primo Romanticismo e del Realismo, ma la struttura propone anche maestri fiamminghi dell&rsquo;età dell&rsquo;oro.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Villa Flora</span></p><p>La residenza della coppia di collezionisti Hahnloser-Bühler era un ritrovo per artisti e amanti dell&rsquo;arte. Oggi, la casa ospita la collezione Arthur &amp; Hedy Hahnloser-Bühler, che vanta opere di Manet, Cézanne e van Gogh.</p><p>Villa Flora riaprirà presumibilmente nel 2022, dopo una ristrutturazione.</p>','Kunst Museum Winterthur','Kunst Museum Winterthur','Kunst Museum Winterthur','Kunst Museum Winterthur','Die drei Häuser des Kunst Museum Winterthur zeigen niederländische Meister bis Gegenwartskunst.','The three museums making up the Kunst Museum Winterthur show Dutch masters to contemporary art.','Expo allant des maîtres néerlandais à l’art contemporain sur les 3 sites du musée de Winterthour.','Il Kunst Museum Winterthur espone opere che spaziano dai maestri fiamminghi all’arte contemporanea.',NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zuerich_kunstmuseum_winterthur_01.jpg','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zurich_culture_villa-flora_01_copyright.jpg','Villa Flora in Winterthur, Aussenansicht','Exterior view of the Villa Flora in Winterthur','2019-10-11 16:24:49 +0200','Ein Ticket für alle drei Standorte','Three museums under one name',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Villa Flora à Winterthour, aspect extérieur','Villa Flora Winterthur, vista esterna',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
